name: Skyscraper //interactive city 1/3
description:
You can left click to rotate right click to move around and scroll wheel to zoom.

On hover of a floor you can see the owners name or address(if they don't have a name) 
This is part 1 of a series of objects that will add up to a whole city.

made with three.js

Note: This building and the owners will be visible in the next 2 parts also!
